Private Sub Display_AnimationStart()
On Error GoTo ErrHandler
Dim INSTRUMENTO As String
INSTRUMENTO = Text1.Caption PONTEIRO_1 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 3, 1) PONTEIRO_2 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 4, 1) PONTEIRO_3 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 7, 1)
If PONTEIRO_1 = "-" Then INSTR_TIPO = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 2) INSTR_NUMERO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 5) End If
If PONTEIRO_2 = "-" Then INSTR_TIPO = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 4) INSTR_NUMERO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 6) End If
If PONTEIRO_3 = "-" Then INSTR_TIPO = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 3) INSTR_NUMERO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 8) End If
AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = " EventSource LIKE '" & INSTR_TIPO & "' And EventSource LIKE '" & INSTR_NUMERO & "'" FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = " SourceName LIKE '%" & INSTR_TIPO & "%' And SourceName LIKE '%" & INSTR_NUMERO & "%'"
Exit Sub ErrHandler: End Sub
Private Sub NumericInput_SP1_KeyDown(ByVal KeyCode As Integer, ByVal Shift As Integer)
If KeyCode = vbKeyReturn Then SendKeys "{F1}" End If
End Sub Private Sub NumericInput_SP2_KeyDown(ByVal KeyCode As Integer, ByVal Shift As Integer)
If KeyCode = vbKeyReturn Then SendKeys "{F2}" End If
End Sub
